    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="/Toto">Auriperto</name>, que Toto vocatur</persName>,
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>
                        riceve da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>,
                        gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine (…), casa et res illa in
                        loco et finibus a <placeName ref="#places/471">Luniano</placeName>, ubi
                        dicitur a Colle, pertenentes <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>, qui est de suppotestatem ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas <persName>quondam <name>Ilpulo</name></persName>
                        ad manus suas abuit; casa vero ipsa cum fundamento et edeficio suo, seo
                        curte, orto ecc. (…). Obbligo: in ipsa casa residere ecc. (…). Censo (pro
                        omni censum ecc.): ad pars ipsius eccl(esie) Sancti Fridiani per sing(ulos)
                        annos per omne mense decembrio (…) ad ipsa eccl(esia) Sancti Fridiani vobis
                        vel ad misso vestro argen(tum) den(arios) bon(os) expend(iviles) numero
                        viginti et sex; et a mandato vestro ecc. (…). Pena: argen(tum) solid(os)
                        viginti (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Ghisolfo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Teudaldus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Ermifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Stefanus">Stefanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>.</ab>
